{
  "texts": [
    "So, there must be emphasis on fairness-aware ML and transparent development, 44 where data are well balanced and representative of all groups, and any patient data are well protected to ensure privacy and security.",
    "Moreover, the widespread adoption of LLMs faces challenges due to cost and resource constraints, particularly in low-resource settings.",
    "45 Addressing this, efficient transfer models and leveraging cloud resources can enhance the accessibility of LLMs.",
    "46 Fostering public-private collaboration can also help distribute costs and resources, facilitating broader adoption.",
    "Given these challenges, additional research is needed to assess the performance of LLMs in clinical VIR."
  ]
}